The tevs directory contains TEVS "Python" files which I have written.  Jimmy 
Frasche is in the process of doing a substantial rewrite.  

The PILB directory contains the files which make up the 
Python Imaging Library, version x.xx, together with extensions 
to that library.  PILB will no removed in the future, replaced
with extensions which make use of PIL's Image structure without 
requiring an extended PIL.

